\vskip1.5cm
\centerline{\titbf Abstract.\hfill}
\ni
We review some attempts of reformulating both gauge theory and general
relativity in terms of holonomy-dependent loop variables. The emphasis
lies on exhibiting the underlying mathematical structures, which often
are not given due attention in physical applications. An extensive list
of references is included.

%\Comment{PACS-0123456789}
\vfill\eject

